+- `Windowed Spectator-Leakage Budget` survives.
+- `Delayed-Threshold Itinerary` remains ambiguous because the scale-separated
+  friendly family does not yet have a uniformly fixed exact `t_next` trace on
+  the current local record.
+
+Return concrete findings, not just file paths, on these exact questions:
+
+1. Which local materials pin the exact Step-4 anti/pro separation margins for
+   `Template-Defect Near-Closure`, including the largest friendly
+   `Delta_tmpl` / `Delta_spec` values and the smallest hostile or failure-side
+   quantities already recorded on the frozen ledger?
+2. Which local materials pin the exact Step-4 anti/pro gap for
+   `Windowed Spectator-Leakage Budget`, including the largest friendly
+   `L_tot`, `L_mirror`, `L_companion`, `L_feedback`, and `L_cross` values and
