+
+## Constraints
+
+- Do not perform Step 6 itself.
+- Do not widen scope beyond the repaired Step-4 dossier.
+- Keep major claims tagged as
+  `[VERIFIED]`,
+  `[INFERRED]`,
+  or
+  `[PROPOSED]`.
