+
+## Goal
+
+Lock the only honest Step-5 repair sheet for
+`Template-Defect Near-Closure`
+and
+`Windowed Spectator-Leakage Budget`.
+
+## What I Tried
+
+- Read the final Step-4 dossier and the landed pro-side arithmetic artifact.
+- Checked which friendly values actually saturate the old thresholds.
+- Repaired only those thresholds that still had unused friendly-side slack.
+
+## Outcome
+
+- `[INFERRED]` `Template-Defect Near-Closure` tightens to
+  `lambda_tmpl = 1/4`
+  and
+  `lambda_spec = 49/256`.
+- `[INFERRED]` `Windowed Spectator-Leakage Budget` tightens to
+  `Lambda_tot = 1/4`,
