+
+- `[VERIFIED]` Inherited Step-4 status:
+  `survives`.
+- `[VERIFIED]` Only allowed repair:
+  tighten
+  `lambda_tmpl`
+  and
+  `lambda_spec`
+  using only the already-recorded Step-4 anti/pro margins.
